<div id="body" style="text-align: justify;">If you seriously want to make it on top of the world of blogging,  you must exert conscious effort to ensure that your blog posts are the  best in the online arena. Here&#8217;s some pints that must be focused :</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Be an expert</strong>. If you want people to listen to you, make sure that you&#8217;ve  got something great to offer. Online users will surely not waste their  time if all you&#8217;ve got is old, general information. So, be an expert on  your niche and strive to be known as one of the greatest sources  information in your chosen field. Perform extensive research as often as  possible and continuously increase your knowledge.<span id="more-153"></span></li>
<li><strong>Be a great  writer</strong>. This is a pre-requisite to become a popular blogger. It&#8217;s a must  that you possess high level writing skills. You can improve your skills  by simply writing as often as you can, by attending writing seminars,  by learning from expert bloggers, and by soliciting writing tips from  the experts from time to time.</li>
<li><strong>Connect with your readers on  emotional level</strong>. People in general simply love it when somebody  understands the things that they are going through. So, empathize when  needed and put yourself in the shoes of your readers when and as needed.  Look at things from their perspective and assure them that you  understand where they are coming from. This is the first step to gain  their trust and loyalty.</li>
<li><strong>Spill the beans.</strong> Your blog will surely  make some serious noise online if you give out trade secrets and  insider tips that other bloggers will not be willing to share.</li>
</ol>
